This Is A Smaug Patch (Code Snippet) for the Classes:  Assassin, Demon,
and Angel. It includes new abilities for each of these classes.

Some Include:

Death Spell
Assassinate Skill
Metallic Skin
Life Force
Lifelift
Reveal
and
Visual Defiance

It also fixes the Possess spell, so that it can be used by demons.
It allows demons to return at will by changing the level of the return
command to 0

It also makes the maximum usable vnum 1,048,575,999 (it can go above this,
but it will not work correctly) and it adds the new undeny command.

It also contains warmboot/copyover.
